title: Someone On The Show Witnessed A Car Accident + We Play Another Round Of 'Never Gonna Get It' + Brothers Osborne Perform In Studio!

description:
Brothers Osborne performed “Stay A Little Longer, in our studio, we all play the unofficial roughest & toughest trivia game in radio, 'Never Gonna Get It' and someone on the show witnessed a car accident! Plus, how would you feel if someone you knew married their stepsister?
